into the highlands.  The trail passes by a tall, seamless black
stone wall to the west.  Shouts in the frost giant language mixes
with shouts in some guttural unintelligible dialect.  The wall
radiates an intense feeling of magic about it.  The trail turns
to the east and heads up into the highlands of the Great Plateau.
