Plateau.  A few assorted weeds manage to grow in the rocky
terrain but not much else.  The snowfall on the plateau is less
harsh due to the magic of Utgard-Loki but is still significant in
the lands not directly under the sway of Utgard.  The Torvald
river is considerably smaller in the highlands and flows by the
city of Utgard below.  The trail appears to be heading up to a
rocky promontory.  The trail can be followed to the west where it
turns along a black stone wall.
